summary: a hotel with lobby, front desk, and at the moment one room.
descriptionHtml:
Contents:
- Front Desk
- Lobby
- Room
- Four Dwemer Beds (not yet usable)
- Long Royal Table
- Eight Royal Chairs (not yet usable)
- Room Key (Keys will get names shortly)

Installation:
- Download and Extract the .zip file
- Place the .esp file in your Data folder (usually located at: \"C:\\Program Files\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\skyrim\\Data\")
- Start Skyrim and make sure the .esp is enabled via \"Data Files\" on the start menu
- Enjoy!

Full Version Spoilers!
- An all new, stand-alone quest.
- Fully usable features in the room.
- Key has a name now.

FULL VERSION IS OUT, DOWNLOAD NOW HERE: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18944
